<#f0f000>Information :</>
Coat Trick can be used to parry 
one hit or projectile as long 
as the coat is between you and 
the opponent

Taunt 						_S

<#f0f000>Information :</>
Bomb Mode:
Use _S in any circumstance
to cycle between Bomb Modes
This only affects the bombs you throw
in that mode
The modes are Remote Controlled and
Time 6s, Time 12s, Time 18s




