<#ff0000>Specials, Supers, Hypers:</>

<#f0f000>Information :</>
Chain Explosions:
Any explosion can trigger another if it hits
another bomb
These explosions damage you as well,
but you recover faster than the enemy
if you weren't being hit
Her burst is also an explosion


